Title: agent_splunk: Make instance an optional parameter
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1580486659
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.0.0i1

The option "Splunk instance to query" in the related WATO rule is now optional.
If not set, the hostname of the explicit host is used.
